M3 done. All gates green.

## What shipped
**Structured outputs** (`app/domain/investigation.py`) — strict Pydantic (`extra="forbid"`, no chain-of-thought leaks): summary, specialist findings, ranked hypotheses, code/commit map, citations, unknowns, contradictions, confidence, falsification tests, rejected claims. Validators enforce contiguous ranks, non-increasing confidence, ≥3 hyps for COMPLETE, remediation-only-when-COMPLETE.

**Bounded specialists + one manager stage** (`app/workflow/investigation_manager.py`) — runs 4 specialists → rejects findings citing unknown evidence → gateway synthesizes draft → re-validates every draft citation → downgrades to INSUFFICIENT_EVIDENCE (disabling remediation) when a COMPLETE draft loses summary/code-map or drops below 3 grounded hyps. Rejected claims recorded, never acted on.

**Golden result** (deterministic) — top hyp: unsafe `session.discount.code` from `c7f2e9a`; code map `src/checkout.ts` + `src/checkout.test.ts` coverage gap; all citations resolve.

**Persistence + API** — `InvestigationReportModel` + migration `c3d5f1a9b024`; `GET /incidents/{id}/investigation`; `/hypotheses` now returns 3 ranked. Pipeline insufficient path stops at `NEEDS_INPUT`, no plan/patch/approval.

**Config** — `INVESTIGATION_MODEL` env-driven, default `simulated-fixture`, no credentials in demo.

